<item>
            <title>[LU-15267] l_getidentity_nss utility</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15267</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A group upcall utility based on l_getidentity.c , which can use all system NSS modules as well as lustre-only user/group configuration in plain files keeping  Lustre users and groups  separate from Linux users/groups on Lustre server&apos;s machines for security reasons.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
